{
  "stem": "1895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 383.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of the family vacations that I remember were in Pionki, because this was the place that my grandfather had an estate-- not an estate, a few acres of land with a couple of buildings on it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a nice place, and I have excellent memories from the summers that we spent there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mostly-- the few summers before the war that I can recall were spent in Pionki-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were other children there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --the hatred of-- the divide between the Poles and the Jews was not as great, somehow, in Pionki, at least not immediately, because the people who lived in the buildings that belonged to my grandfather considered me their landlord, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had, somehow, a little respect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was not physically afraid of anybody on a daily basis, like I was back in Radom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Back in Radom, as soon as I left my house, I went downstairs, I had to watch out for these hooligans, for the Polish boys.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Pionki, I was a little more relaxed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had wonderful, wonderful days-- wonderful, most wonderful days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a big lake in Pionki where my father taught me how to swim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had friends, and I would leave the house about 8 in the morning every day and go to that lake and spend it with my friends, and come back at 2 o'clock in the afternoon to have a bite to eat, and then run right back to that lake.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a little boat that I and a friend of mine built.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His father was in the hardware business.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
